    <item>
      <title>雀巢分析师在下调评级时质问“我们做错了什么？”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/nestle-analysts-ask-what-did-we-get-wrong-as-they-cut-ratings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[雀巢公司 (Nestle SA) 的分析师纷纷下调对该股的评级，担心这家消费品公司将难以实现利润增长，导致其获得了四年来最负面的一致评级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/nestle-analysts-ask-what-did-we-get-wrong-as-they-cut-ratings</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 13:15:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国 6 月份核心 PCE 上涨 0.2%，支出保持坚挺</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-26/us-core-pce-rises-0-2-in-june-personal-spending-remains-firm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[核心个人消费支出价格指数是美联储衡量潜在通胀的首选指标，6 月份该指数上涨 0.2%，较上年同期上涨 2.6%。迈克尔·麦基在彭博电视台上对这些数字进行了详细分析。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-26/us-core-pce-rises-0-2-in-june-personal-spending-remains-firm</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 13:03:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国电力公司首席执行官称法国太阳能补贴需要严格审查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/edf-chief-says-french-solar-power-subsidies-need-scrutiny</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国电力公司首席执行官吕克·雷蒙特 (Luc Remont) 敦促法国政策制定者重新审查对太阳能发电的补贴，称这些措施会增加电网的发电量，并在电力需求持续低迷的情况下损害这家核电巨头的财务状况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/edf-chief-says-french-solar-power-subsidies-need-scrutiny</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 13:00:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>数据支持 9 月降息，美国国债价格上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/treasuries-rally-as-data-backs-the-case-for-a-september-rate-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美联储最青睐的通胀指标巩固了交易员对九月份降息的预期，美国国债价格在动荡的一周结束时上涨。]]></description>
